Package com.immunet.immunet.model

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.immunet.immunet.model.Person
com.immunet.immunet.model.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Doctor
public class User extends Person
Represents a user in the system, extending the Person class with additional user-specific properties such as username, password, and billing address. This class is used to manage user account details.
